<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />For you are my rock and my fortress;</para>

<para style="q1">therefore for your name's sake, lead and guide me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Pluck me out of the net that they have hidden for me,</para>

<para style="q1">for you are my refuge.</para>
